{"tid":1572040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［賽後檢討］私了手法不完美可接受 入黎一齊改善","createTime":"2019-09-15T14:44:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T18:04:32.000Z","uid":4482,"like":138,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"8a4eebeb22a61b3691690dd845f9fcfe1dd14fdf","tid":1572040,"uid":4482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:44:28.000Z","msg":"見好多手足依然打頭/肌肉，無錯你見佢爆曬缸好爽，但佢地只要抖返幾日/最多一個月，消腫後就可以再出黎破壞<br />\n做左三十幾年運動經驗，最怕其實係關節/韌帶，強如伊巴謙莫域都要抖9個月，我呢啲非職業玩玩下，閒閒地要一年半，班廢老新陳代謝再慢啲，行唔行得返都成問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幻想圖: 膝頭hyper extend<br />\n當廢老仆親，抬起隻腳，反向踩落去，會令膝頭入面啲野斷，千其唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a1yWzg6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa1yWzg6.jpg&h=ec2e3e29&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ded5e16e9df532cc6affc16e73ddd7f37d1aca8a","tid":1572040,"uid":4482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:45:22.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"2698b0b2f1a1aa7aae095d6b0700d6931395856b","tid":1572040,"uid":4482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:45:32.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"e9253dd5937b9c7e364605bcdec15ac988779c2a","tid":1572040,"uid":166080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:45:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f37897c59aa6534a7e62de6bad300a70487985d","tid":1572040,"uid":4482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:45:50.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"24641f3d4f9b08d070e2e8cb321d52a3a76ac265","tid":1572040,"uid":4482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:46:00.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"d848c062b75c51882db66112bfdb162658ea7a8a","tid":1572040,"uid":4482,"like":0,"dislik