www.facebook.com%2Fpassiontimes%2Fvideos%2F2529038127353535%2FUzpfSTM5Njk0OTQzMzgxMjc1MzoxMjkwNjAxMDU0NDQ3NTgy%2F&d=Vjn4Al6Q2mdpb7%2BU1BdqDgDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=8f6e6980\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/passiontimes/videos/2529038127353535/UzpfSTM5Njk0OTQzMzgxMjc1MzoxMjkwNjAxMDU0NDQ3NTgy/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:07:27.000Z","msg":"撲埋去個下好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6c8382bc056fd3047b600395a5630c8d7b1bf95","tid":1572040,"uid":123914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:07:58.000Z","msg":"關節關節"},{"pid":"f8cbb4568f881e1214ee8430996cb8f728de0392","tid":1572040,"uid":63651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:13:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好痛 唔好咁做呀千奇唔好推"},{"pid":"c110f66bd32c73e3a6fb51ac192c62ba6df310f0","tid":1572040,"uid":269967,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7e1d5d02d3d920f02ac96d044a6b863fca41e882","tid":1572040,"uid":78392,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:46:28.000Z","msg":"無人私了呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係班藍絲誤中自己人！！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:18:25.000Z","msg":"警方fc 冇打鬥 伙記黎<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】北角晚上多次出現打鬥，有示威者在炮台山被追打。警員曾截查涉嫌打人的男子，但未有即場拘捕，將他放走。<br />\n<br />\n一批男人在近北角英皇道聚集，地上放有長竹，警員曾上前勸他們返回行人路，但他們未有理會，一直跟隨警員推進。<br />\n<br />\n去到炮台山，<span style=\"color: red;\">其中一人用摺椅襲擊其他人，一批警員到場。該批施襲的男人退到警員的後面，一會兒後，繼續與警員一起推進。</span><br />\n<br />\n去炮台山，再追打幾名黑衣人入港鐵站。回到地面，用摺椅擊打另一人的頭部。大批防暴警員到場制止，<span style=\"color: red;\">將用摺椅施襲的白衣男人帶到一邊，截查一段時間後將他放走</span>，有途人不滿。<br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂，多名男子推另一名男士，警員到場將懷疑推人的男子帶上警車，警員亦在現場帶走多名相信是示威者。<br />\n<br />\n一段時間後，早前用摺椅施襲的一批人士繼續在北角街頭出現。一名警員曾上前想阻止他們全部離開，但不成功。<br />\n<br />\n北角晚上多次出現打鬥，防暴警察在場戒備。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=362858&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D362858%26refer%3D&d=Vjn4Al6Q2mdpb7%2BU1BdqDgDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=508d5b7f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D362858%26refer%3D&h=3ed08434\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=362858&amp;refer=</a>"},{"pid":"12b8e387b011cdb2be29ad198f36873a2398c691","tid":1572040,"uid":164851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7be468a082e2a49b648e3e15cdef37a1e2effd9a","tid":1572040,"uid":294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:50:54.000Z","msg":"2:50秒,<br />\n<br />\n有個後生仔比廢老偷襲<br />\n之後個後生仔一野撲埋去落佢單, 跟住個廢老比人圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/passiontimes/videos/2529038127353535/UzpfSTM5Njk0OTQzMzgxMjc1MzoxMjkwNjAxMDU0NDQ3NTgy/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpassiontimes%2Fvideos%2F2529038127353535%2FUzpfSTM5Njk0OTQzMzgxMjc1MzoxMjkwNjAxMDU0NDQ3NTgy%2F&d=Vjn4Al6Q2mdpb7%2BU1BdqDgDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=8f6e6980\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/passiontimes/videos/2529038127353535/UzpfSTM5Njk0OTQzMzgxMjc1MzoxMjkwNjAxMDU0NDQ3NTgy/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:18:44.000Z","msg":"踩爆佢春袋啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c45bd9054d9cd55680ea4ab07dc2102ea058c22b","tid":1572040,"uid":4482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:18:58.000Z","msg":"祝藍絲百病纏身，長命百歲，返大灣區醫病<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d87df584b42b9bc3fa93db286cd9f1e02bbbfe0","tid":1572040,"uid":123914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"